wiki.summary: "SPOT!" is a song by the South Korean singer ZICO featuring JENNIE, a member of BLACKPINK. Released on April 26, 2024, under KOZ Entertainment and HYBE Labels, it marks the first collaboration between the two artists and JENNIE's debut appearance in HYBE Productions. Read more on Last.fm.
